
  Dragapult    Dragon Type Pokémon

  When it isn’t battling, it keeps 
  Dreepy in the holes on its horns. 
   Once a fight starts, it launches 
  the Dreepy like supersonic missiles. 
  
	   Evolution Chain
  Dreepy ► Drakloak ► Dragapult

